<emphasis id="B94BEA910D23FFF3C205C6E980C2E7FE" box="[260,426,1734,1755]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="209">Vochysia sobralii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. 
<emphasis id="B94BEA910D23FFF3C2B7C6E980A6E7FE" bold="true" box="[438,462,1734,1755]" pageId="2" pageNumber="209">A.</emphasis>
Flowering branch. 
<emphasis id="B94BEA910D23FFF3C188C6E883C8E7F9" bold="true" box="[649,672,1735,1756]" pageId="2" pageNumber="209">B.</emphasis>
Nodal region, showing stipules. 
<emphasis id="B94BEA910D23FFF3C0DCC6E9829CE7F9" bold="true" box="[989,1012,1734,1756]" pageId="2" pageNumber="209">C.</emphasis>
