<subSubSection id="C32565080D23FFF3C3BCC7588579E904" pageId="2" pageNumber="209" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8B8036830D23FFF3C3BCC7588579E904" blockId="2.[136,1452,1911,2081]" pageId="2" pageNumber="209">
<emphasis id="B94BEA910D23FFF3C3BCC758802DE6B4" bold="true" box="[189,325,1911,1937]" pageId="2" pageNumber="209">Discussion:</emphasis>
—Within 
<taxonomicName id="4C3F4D000D23FFF3C2B7C758838BE6B4" authorityName="Ducke" authorityYear="1938" box="[438,739,1911,1937]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Vochysiaceae" genus="Vochysia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Myrtales" pageId="2" pageNumber="209" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="section" section="Pachyantha">
<emphasis id="B94BEA910D23FFF3C2B7C7588372E6B4" box="[438,538,1911,1937]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="209">Vochysia</emphasis>
sect. 
<emphasis id="B94BEA910D23FFF3C15CC758838BE6B4" box="[605,739,1911,1937]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="209">Pachyantha</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C3F4D000D23FFF3C1F3C75882DDE6B4" box="[754,949,1911,1937]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Vochysiaceae" genus="Vochysia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Myrtales" pageId="2" pageNumber="209" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="sobralii">
<emphasis id="B94BEA910D23FFF3C1F3C75882DDE6B4" box="[754,949,1911,1937]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="209">Vochysia sobralii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is more similar to 
<taxonomicName id="4C3F4D000D23FFF3C791C7578598E6B4" authorityName="Marcano-Berti &amp; Poncy" authorityYear="2016" box="[1168,1264,1911,1937]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Vochysiaceae" genus="Vochysia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Myrtales" pageId="2" pageNumber="209" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="sofiae">
<emphasis id="B94BEA910D23FFF3C791C7578598E6B4" box="[1168,1264,1911,1937]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="209">V. sofiae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, due to the long petioles, large leaves, and cuspidate leaf apex. But it differs in the cuneate leaf base (vs. obtuse or rounded in 
<taxonomicName id="4C3F4D000D23FFF3C645C7B384CAE690" authorityName="Marcano-Berti &amp; Poncy" authorityYear="2016" box="[1348,1442,1947,1973]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Vochysiaceae" genus="Vochysia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Myrtales" pageId="2" pageNumber="209" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="sofiae">
<emphasis id="B94BEA910D23FFF3C645C7B384CAE690" box="[1348,1442,1947,1973]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="209">V. sofiae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
) and acute flower bud apex (vs. obtuse). Also, 
<taxonomicName id="4C3F4D000D23FFF3C181C7EF839AE6FC" box="[640,754,1983,2009]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Vochysiaceae" genus="Vochysia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Myrtales" pageId="2" pageNumber="209" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="sobralii">
<emphasis id="B94BEA910D23FFF3C181C7EF839AE6FC" box="[640,754,1983,2009]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="209">V. sobralii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
occurs in southern 
<collectingRegion id="49FBF8610D23FFF3C0C8C7908296E6FC" box="[969,1022,1983,2009]" country="Brazil" name="Para" pageId="2" pageNumber="209">Pará</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingCountry id="F32876130D23FFF3C709C7908527E6FC" box="[1032,1103,1983,2009]" name="Brazil" pageId="2" pageNumber="209">Brazil</collectingCountry>
, ca. 
<quantity id="4CC79B660D23FFF3C77EC7908580E6FC" box="[1151,1256,1983,2010]" metricMagnitude="6" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.5" pageId="2" pageNumber="209" unit="km" value="1500.0">1,500 km</quantity>
apart from Saint-Georges-de-l’Oyapock, 
<collectingCountry id="F32876130D23FFF3C297C7CC8356E6D8" box="[406,574,2019,2045]" name="French Guiana" pageId="2" pageNumber="209">French Guiana</collectingCountry>
, where 
<taxonomicName id="4C3F4D000D23FFF3C195C7CB839AE6D8" authorityName="Marcano-Berti &amp; Poncy" authorityYear="2016" box="[660,754,2019,2045]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Vochysiaceae" genus="Vochysia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Myrtales" pageId="2" pageNumber="209" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="sofiae">
<emphasis id="B94BEA910D23FFF3C195C7CB839AE6D8" box="[660,754,2019,2045]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="209">V. sofiae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was collected. A dichotomous key and a link to a multi-access interactive key for all ten species of the section 
<taxonomicName id="4C3F4D000D23FFF3C19FC828824CE904" authorityName="Ducke" authorityYear="1938" box="[670,804,2055,2081]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Vochysiaceae" genus="Vochysia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Myrtales" pageId="2" pageNumber="209" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="section" section="Pachyantha">
<emphasis id="B94BEA910D23FFF3C19FC828824CE904" box="[670,804,2055,2081]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="209">Pachyantha</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
are presented below.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</treatment>
